data.description: Only 45 minutes to Eagle Road exit! This hard-to-find 5 bedroom, 3 bathroom home features a fully finished basement situated in a charming, quiet neighborhood on a large corner lot. The spacious living room boasts a big gas fireplace, perfect for cozy evenings at home. Enjoy the master suite plus 2 generous-sized rooms and a full bath on the main floor and 2 bedrooms and a full bath and a family room in the basement. There's plenty of space and comfort for loved ones, easy entertaining, plus privacy and room for all your toys! The partially covered back patio is great for entertaining so get your grill and come on over to see this beauty. Updates include new HVAC, new floor coverings, an updated master bathroom, and more! centrally located in Ontario, Oregon where you'll be close to schools, shopping, and hospitals along with easy access to I-84 or Hwy 201.
